## Memory

- Save all memories to .memory/
- Every file must have YAML frontmatter: title, tags, date
- Keep the file content concise, only core conclusions, reusable snippets, key decisions
- All references use [[wiki-link]] to existing files
- Same topic must be merged or cross-linked, never duplicate
- After save, automatically maintain .memory/index.md
